# dev-only: local node_modules for lint tooling (biome) and the staged
# platform package that lets the pi extension shim require.resolve the Go
# binary during `pi install` of the source tree. Never published (npm
# excludes node_modules; files whitelist is bin/ + extensions/).
node_modules/
